    "9": {
      "title": "section_9",
      "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Main_Hall:_AquariumCC\"><span id=\"Main_Hall:_Aquarium\"></span>Main Hall: Aquarium<sup style=\"line-height:1.0\"><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Fishing\" title=\"Skyrim:Fishing\">CC</a></sup></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Skyrim:Main_Hall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Main Hall: AquariumCC\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>With the <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Fishing\" title=\"Skyrim:Fishing\">Fishing</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Creation Club\">Creation</a> installed, an eastern hallway is added to the north room of the <a href=\"#Main_Hall:_Cellar\">Cellar</a>. Using the Cellar's Carpenter's Workbench, you will have the option to construct an Aquarium. This adds a new room at the end of the hallway with plenty of space for fish tanks and related paraphernalia.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"6\">Main Hall, Aquarium - Furnishings\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Type</th>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Options</th>\n<th>Materials</th>\n<th>Notes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Containers\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Pages_Missing_Data\" title=\"Category:Pages Missing Data\"><sup>need icon</sup></a></td>\n<td>Fishing Supplies</td>\n<td>Sawn Log, Nails, Iron Ingot</td>\n<td>East wall, north side. Adds two fish barrels containing usual items, a knapsack containing <a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Skyrim:Fishing_Clothes&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Skyrim:Fishing Clothes (page does not exist)\">fishing clothes</a> and <a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Skyrim:Fishing_Hat&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Skyrim:Fishing Hat (page does not exist)\">hat</a>, a satchel containing 2 <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Pearl\" title=\"Skyrim:Pearl\">pearls</a> and 6 <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Small_Pearl\" title=\"Skyrim:Small Pearl\">small pearls</a>, a <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Fishing_Rod\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Fishing Rod\">fishing rod</a>, a pair of <a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Skyrim:Fishing_Boots&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Skyrim:Fishing Boots (page does not exist)\">fishing boots</a>, and 2 <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Salmon_Roe\" title=\"Skyrim:Salmon Roe\">salmon roe</a>, 4 <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Nordic_Barnacle\" title=\"Skyrim:Nordic Barnacle\">nordic barnacles</a>, and 5 <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Slaughterfish_Egg\" title=\"Skyrim:Slaughterfish Egg\">slaughterfish eggs</a>.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-construction-Cupboard.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-construction-Cupboard.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/1/14/SR-icon-construction-Cupboard.png/48px-SR-icon-construction-Cupboard.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/1/14/SR-icon-construction-Cupboard.png/72px-SR-icon-construction-Cupboard.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/1/14/SR-icon-construction-Cupboard.png/96px-SR-icon-construction-Cupboard.png 2x\" /></a></td>\n<td>Cupboard</td>\n<td>2 Sawn Log, 4 Nails, Iron Fittings</td>\n<td>Hallway, south wall, east of center.\n</td></tr>\n<tr style=\"border-top:solid 2px\">\n<th rowspan=\"6\">Furniture\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Pages_Missing_Data\" title=\"Category:Pages Missing Data\"><sup>need icon</sup></a></td>\n<td>Large Fish Tank</td>\n<td>Quarried Stone, Clay, Glass</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Pages_Missing_Data\" title=\"Category:Pages Missing Data\"><sup>need notes</sup></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Pages_Missing_Data\" title=\"Category:Pages Missing Data\"><sup>need icon</sup></a></td>\n<td>Large Fish Tanks (2)</td>\n<td>Quarried Stone, 2 Clay, 2 Glass</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Pages_Missing_Data\" title=\"Category:Pages Missing Data\"><sup>need notes</sup></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Large Fish Tanks (2)</td>\n<td>Quarried Stone, 2 Clay, 2 Glass</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Pages_Missing_Data\" title=\"Category:Pages Missing Data\"><sup>need notes</sup></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Pages_Missing_Data\" title=\"Category:Pages Missing Data\"><sup>need icon</sup></a></td>\n<td>Small Fish Tanks (2)</td>\n<td>Sawn Log, 2 Nails, 2 Glass</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Pages_Missing_Data\" title=\"Category:Pages Missing Data\"><sup>need notes</sup></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Small Fish Tanks (2)</td>\n<td>Sawn Log, 2 Nails, 2 Glass</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Pages_Missing_Data\" title=\"Category:Pages Missing Data\"><sup>need notes</sup></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Small Fish Tanks (2)</td>\n<td>Sawn Log, 2 Nails, 2 Glass</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Pages_Missing_Data\" title=\"Category:Pages Missing Data\"><sup>need notes</sup></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr style=\"border-top:solid 2px\">\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Shelves\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-construction-Tall_Shelf.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-construction-Tall Shelf.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/4/48/SR-icon-construction-Tall_Shelf.png/48px-SR-icon-construction-Tall_Shelf.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/4/48/SR-icon-construction-Tall_Shelf.png/72px-SR-icon-construction-Tall_Shelf.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/4/48/SR-icon-construction-Tall_Shelf.png/96px-SR-icon-construction-Tall_Shelf.png 2x\" /></a></td>\n<td>Tall Shelf</td>\n<td>2 Sawn Log, 4 Nails</td>\n<td>Hallway, south wall, east side. Adds 3 bottles of <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Surilie_Brothers_Wine\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Surilie Brothers Wine\">Surilie Brothers Wine</a><sup><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Hearthfire\" title=\"Skyrim:Hearthfire\">HF</a></sup>, 2 bottles of <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Argonian_Bloodwine\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Argonian Bloodwine\">Argonian Bloodwine</a><sup><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Hearthfire\" title=\"Skyrim:Hearthfire\">HF</a></sup>, and some <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Wine\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Wine\">Wine</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Alto_Wine\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Alto Wine\">Alto Wine</a>.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-construction-Wall_Shelves.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-construction-Wall Shelves.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/4/4c/SR-icon-construction-Wall_Shelves.png/48px-SR-icon-construction-Wall_Shelves.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/4/4c/SR-icon-construction-Wall_Shelves.png/72px-SR-icon-construction-Wall_Shelves.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/4/4c/SR-icon-construction-Wall_Shelves.png/96px-SR-icon-construction-Wall_Shelves.png 2x\" /></a></td>\n<td>Wall Shelf</td>\n<td>Sawn Log, Nails</td>\n<td>Hallway, north wall, east side. Adds sack on floor below.\n</td></tr>\n<tr style=\"border-top:solid 2px\">\n<th rowspan=\"8\">Misc\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Pages_Missing_Data\" title=\"Category:Pages Missing Data\"><sup>need icon</sup></a></td>\n<td>Aquarium</td>\n<td>4 Sawn Log, 25 Quarried Stone</td>\n<td>Expansion east of the main rooms.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Pages_Missing_Data\" title=\"Category:Pages Missing Data\"><sup>need icon</sup></a></td>\n<td>Fish Plaques (3)</td>\n<td>Sawn Log, Nails</td>\n<td>East wall, south side, above pair of Small Fish Tanks.<a href=\"/wiki/Category:Pages_Missing_Data\" title=\"Category:Pages Missing Data\"><sup>need notes</sup></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Fish Plaques (3)</td>\n<td>Sawn Log, Nails</td>\n<td>West wall, south side, above pair of Small Fish Tanks.<a href=\"/wiki/Category:Pages_Missing_Data\" title=\"Category:Pages Missing Data\"><sup>need notes</sup></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Fish Plaques (3)</td>\n<td>Sawn Log, Nails</td>\n<td>South wall,  above pair of Small Fish Tanks. One different style.<a href=\"/wiki/Category:Pages_Missing_Data\" title=\"Category:Pages Missing Data\"><sup>need notes</sup></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-construction-Mounted_Mudcrab.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-construction-Mounted Mudcrab.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/6/6a/SR-icon-construction-Mounted_Mudcrab.png/48px-SR-icon-construction-Mounted_Mudcrab.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/6/6a/SR-icon-construction-Mounted_Mudcrab.png/72px-SR-icon-construction-Mounted_Mudcrab.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/6/6a/SR-icon-construction-Mounted_Mudcrab.png/96px-SR-icon-construction-Mounted_Mudcrab.png 2x\" /></a></td>\n<td>Mounted Mudcrab</td>\n<td>Leather Strips, 2 Mudcrab Chitin</td>\n<td>North wall, above Large Fish Tank.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-construction-Wall_Sconces.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-construction-Wall Sconces.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/6/6b/SR-icon-construction-Wall_Sconces.png/48px-SR-icon-construction-Wall_Sconces.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/6/6b/SR-icon-construction-Wall_Sconces.png/72px-SR-icon-construction-Wall_Sconces.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/6/6b/SR-icon-construction-Wall_Sconces.png/96px-SR-icon-construction-Wall_Sconces.png 2x\" /></a></td>\n<td>Wall Sconce</td>\n<td>Iron Fittings, Goat Horns</td>\n<td>Hallway, north side.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Wall Sconce (2)</td>\n<td>Iron Fittings, Goat Horns</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Pages_Missing_Data\" title=\"Category:Pages Missing Data\"><sup>need notes</sup></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Wall Sconce (2)</td>\n<td>Iron Fittings, Goat Horns</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Pages_Missing_Data\" title=\"Category:Pages Missing Data\"><sup>need notes</sup></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr style=\"border-top:solid 2px\">\n<th>Total Materials:\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"4\"><i>5 <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Clay\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Clay\">Clay</a>, 11 <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Glass\" class=\"mw-disambig\" title=\"Skyrim:Glass\">Glass</a>, 3 <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Goat_Horns\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Goat Horns\">Goat Horns</a>, 4 <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Iron_Fittings\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Iron Fittings\">Iron Fittings</a>, 1 <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Iron_Ingot\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Iron Ingot\">Iron Ingot</a>, 1 <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Leather_Strips\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Leather Strips\">Leather Strips</a>, 2 <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Mudcrab_Chitin\" title=\"Skyrim:Mudcrab Chitin\">Mudcrab Chitin</a>, 19 <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Nails\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Nails\">Nails</a>, 28 <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Quarried_Stone\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Quarried Stone\">Quarried Stone</a>, 16 <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Sawn_Log\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Sawn Log\">Sawn Logs</a></i>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by content2.uesp.net\nCached time: 20260720152109\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.023 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.055 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 632/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5388/8388608 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 537/8388608 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 5/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/1000\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 76/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   22.166      1 -total\n 24.64%    5.461     17 Template:Huh\n 20.76%    4.602      5 Template:Icon\n 15.14%    3.355      1 Template:CC\n 14.69%    3.256      1 Template:Anchor\n 13.90%    3.080      2 Template:HF\n 12.05%    2.672      5 Template:Icon_Abbr\n  8.06%    1.786      4 Template:ThickLine\n-->\n</div>"
